OL,3,CPolice officer could face criminal
OL,4,Ccharges after pensioner killed in crash
OL,6,FThe police watchdog has found that an
OL,7,Fofficer may have committed a criminal
OL,8,Foffence after a pensioner died when a
OL,9,Fpolice van collided into him while he
OL,10,Fwas crossing the road.
OL,12,FTrevor Bartlett, 80, who was a retired
OL,13,Fnewspaper photographer, died after the
OL,14,Fcollision which happened while he was
OL,15,Fusing a pedestrian crossing on the A52
OL,16,FDerby Road in Beeston, Nottingham, on
OL,17,FDecember 19 2023.
