OL,3,CPolice officer could face criminal
OL,4,Ccharges after pensioner killed in crash
OL,6,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,7,FConduct (IOPC) said it found that the
OL,8,Fpolice vehicle was taking a detainee
OL,9,Fto a custody facility and was
OL,10,Ftravelling in a bus lane with blue
OL,11,Flights and sirens on at the time.
OL,13,FThe driver, a Nottinghamshire Police
OL,14,Fconstable, was interviewed by the IOPC
OL,15,Funder criminal caution for the
OL,16,Fpotential offences of causing death by
OL,17,Fdangerous driving and causing death by
OL,18,Fcareless or inconsiderate driving.
