OL,3,CPolice officer could face criminal
OL,4,Ccharges after pensioner killed in crash
OL,6,FThe IOPC said it has referred the case
OL,7,Fto the Crown Prosecution Service (CPS)
OL,8,Fto consider criminal charges.
OL,10,FThe officer was served with a notice
OL,11,Fof investigation for gross misconduct
OL,12,Fand the watchdog said a disciplinary
OL,13,Fhearing will be arranged by the police
OL,14,Fforce.
