OL,3,CPolice officer could face criminal
OL,4,Ccharges after pensioner killed in crash
OL,6,FIOPC director Derrick Campbell said:
OL,7,F"Following thorough and careful
OL,8,Fanalysis of all the evidence, we have
OL,9,Fdecided there is an indication an
OL,10,Fofficer may have committed a criminal
OL,11,Foffence in relation to the manner of
OL,12,Ftheir driving and a file has been
OL,13,Freferred to the Crown Prosecution
OL,14,FService.
OL,16,F"I am satisfied we have gathered all
OL,17,Fthe available evidence and it is now
OL,18,Ffor the CPS to consider whether to
OL,19,Fbring criminal charges.
